hopobject.body: I work with computers nitric alpha no2 free trial Thus Hummel sponsors Afghanistan’s national football teams, founded a football training academy in Sierra Leone in 2010 and supports a local team in Christiana, the hippy commune in Copenhagen. “Nike, Puma, adidas – those big brands can’t sponsor the Afghanistan team because for them it’s too dangerous, too political, but as a smaller brand we can,” says Stadil. Would he class himself as a hippy? “At some point, yes, but I like to make money.”
